    <h2>Workshops</h2> 
<p>Consent Comes First works with campus partners to provide the Ryerson community with education, prevention, training and awareness activities. To book a workshop email <a href="osvse@ryerson.ca" target="_blank">osvse@ryerson.ca.<span aria-hidden="true" class="autoIconLink fa fa-external-link"></span><span class="sr-only">, opens in new window</span></a></p>
    





