            <div class="panel panel-default">
                <!-- Accordion Heading -->
                <div class="panel-heading container-clipboard">
                    <div class="panel-title">
                        <a id="accordion-1528817046987-consent-comes-first--addressing-sexual-harassment-in-the-workplace" role="tab" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#" href="#accordion-content-1528817046987-consent-comes-first--addressing-sexual-harassment-in-the-workplace" aria-controls="accordion-content-1528817046987-consent-comes-first--addressing-sexual-harassment-in-the-workplace" aria-expanded="false">
                            Consent Comes First: Addressing Sexual Harassment in the Workplace
                        </a>
                    </div>
                    
                </div>
                <!-- Accordion Body -->
                <div tabindex="0" id="accordion-content-1528817046987-consent-comes-first--addressing-sexual-harassment-in-the-workplace" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="accordion-1528817046987-consent-comes-first--addressing-sexual-harassment-in-the-workplace">
                    <div class="panel-body ">
                        <div class="1528817046987 stackparsys">










				
				<div class="resText parbase section">


























<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="d5c78533-62ed-4b0f-a42e-a8bcb80db736" >

    <p>Sexual harassment in the workplace is never okay. In this training, participants will learn the different forms of sexual harassment that can occur in the workplace, how to practice consent in the workplace and relevance policies related to workplace safety such as Ryerson Sexual &nbsp;Violence Policy, Occupational Health and Safety Act. Participants will also learn about bystander intervention as part of TakeCareRU campaign and how to connect to supports for staff and faculty on and off campus.</p>
    





</div>
<script>$(document).ready(function(){addCoursePopover("#d5c78533-62ed-4b0f-a42e-a8bcb80db736");});</script></div>

				</div>

                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
        </div>
    </div>
